Quick Example

Upload Sales Data and Get Forecast
// Install the SDK
npm install @ordernimbus/sdk

// Initialize client
import { OrderNimbusClient } from '@ordernimbus/sdk';

const client = new OrderNimbusClient({
  apiKey: 'your-api-key',
  environment: 'production' // or 'sandbox'
});

// Upload sales data
const salesData = [
  {
    date: '2024-01-01',
    productId: 'SKU-001',
    quantity: 25,
    revenue: 500.00,
    storeId: 'store-1'
  }
  // ... more data
];

await client.data.upload(salesData);

// Generate forecast
const forecast = await client.forecasting.predict({
  storeId: 'store-1',
  horizon: 30, // 30 days
  confidence: 0.95
});

console.log('Forecast:', forecast);
